\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Loot is the heart of the game\'92s progression, and we design the entire reward loop to feel like a 
\f1\b gift-filled arcade experience
\f0\b0 . Throughout the run, players will be showered with rewards: from coins flying out of enemies to treasure chests in hidden corners. The key is to make these rewards 
\f1\b frequent and satisfying
\f0\b0  (lots of shiny pick-ups, fanfare on collection) without trivializing the difficulty. We achieve this with varied loot types and a clear upgrade path for each.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 Loot Types:
\f0\b0  The game will include:\
