\f0\b0  Commonly dropped by enemies and found in breakable objects. Coins are used to purchase upgrades or items between runs (meta-progression) and possibly to spend at occasional in-run shops or on checkpoints. Coin drops often come in 
\f1\b bursts
\f0\b0  \'96 e.g. killing a group of enemies might spawn a fountain of coins that 
\f3\i explode
\f0\i0  outward, which the player can run through to collect (this \'93coin explosion\'94 effect is visually rewarding and taps into that dopamine loop of seeing loot fly everywhere).\
