\f0\b0  The Heads-Up Display should convey important info (health, score, currency, skill cooldowns) without clutter. Following endless runner best practices, keep elements to the corners and edges so as not to block the action. For instance, display the score or distance in a corner in a clear font. You can incorporate subtle animations in the HUD: e.g. the score text could flash or grow when the player hits a new high score or reaches a milestone (as suggested, color transitions at milestones to celebrate progress. The gift theme can show up in HUD icons \'96 for example, a small gift icon next to the currency count or as the icon for loot pickups.\
