\f0\b0  Show the player\'92s health bar prominently (top-left or top-center). If the player has armor or a shield buff, an icon or a secondary bar could indicate that. During boss fights, display the boss\'92s health bar at the top of the screen, with the boss\'92s name. This gives the fight a dramatic feel and lets the player gauge progress in the fight.\
